<TEXT>
GOLD shares reacted cautiously to bullion's late rise through the Dollars
370 an ounce level and the index added 16 at 1,770. Industrials lost 10 to
4,490, with Richemont dipping 45 cents to R37.40. The overall index eased 5
to 3,896.
